sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor User as AnalystUser
participant Client as WebClient
participant AiApi as AiTaskService
participant AiDb as MongoAiTaskExtraction
participant Queue as RabbitMQ
participant Worker as AiTaskWorker
participant Llm as OllamaModel
participant TaskApi as TaskService
participant SyncDb as MongoSyncSuggestion
User->>Client: Yeu cau trich xuat task tu message
Client->>AiApi: POST /api/ai-tasks/extract
AiApi->>AiDb: save extraction status=queued
AiApi->>Queue: publish task-ai.extract
AiApi-->>Client: 202 accepted
Queue->>Worker: consume extract job
Worker->>Llm: infer draft task + confidence
Worker->>AiDb: update extraction completed
User->>Client: Xac nhan tao task that
Client->>AiApi: POST /api/ai-tasks/confirm + Idempotency-Key
AiApi->>TaskApi: create task
alt Confirm hop le
  AiApi->>AiDb: mark confirmed
  AiApi-->>Client: 201 task created
else Duplicate key / task service error
  AiApi-->>Client: 409/5xx
end
Note over Worker,SyncDb: message sua/xoa se tao sync suggestion
